Mombasa Governor Hassan Joho hosted Muslims from the county to an iftar dinner at the Serena grounds last Friday.Â Present were NASA leader Raila Odinga, who was the chief guest, accompanied by his elder brother Eala MP Oburu Odinga and Suna East MP Junet Mohammed. Raila called on coast residents to support the handshake, revealing that Mombasa will the first stop for him and President Uhuru Kenyatta in their countrywide campaign to preach peace and bring Kenyans together.